arts.ttl: Confirmed Lineups: Germany U19 v Netherlands U19
arts.sum: The lineups are out for Germany’s first U19 Euros game in eight years.

arts.ttl: Germany U19 vs Netherlands U19 preview: Team news & predicted lineups – U19 Euros 2025
arts.sum: In parallel with the more popular U21 tournament, UEFA’s U19 competition starts on Friday in Romania. Germany will start their journey against the Netherlands in a tricky group.
